## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="6ca75-103">고유 이름의 확장 된 폼의 개체 objectGUID 속성의 문자열 표현을 포함합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6ca75-103">The extended form of a distinguished name includes a string representation of the objectGUID property of an object.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="6ca75-104">사용자, 그룹 및 컴퓨터와 같은 보안 주체 개체에 대 한 확장된 된 형식 objectSID 속성의 문자열 표현을 포함 되어 있습니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6ca75-104">For security principal objects such as users, groups, and computers, the extended form also includes a string representation of the objectSID property.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="6ca75-105">ObjectSID 및 objectGUID 속성에 대 한 자세한 내용은 항목을 참조 하십시오. [개체 Guid](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/default.asp?url=/library/adschema/adschema/a_objectguid.asp) 및 [개체 Sid](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/default.asp?url=/library/adschema/adschema/a_objectguid.asp) MSDN library에서 [ http://msdn.microsoft.com/library ](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library)합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6ca75-105">For more information about the objectGUID and objectSID properties, see the topics [Object-Guid](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/default.asp?url=/library/adschema/adschema/a_objectguid.asp) and [Object-Sid](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/default.asp?url=/library/adschema/adschema/a_objectguid.asp) in the MSDN Library at [http://msdn.microsoft.com/library](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library).</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="6ca75-106">다음 C# 예제에서는 16 진수 형식의 고유 이름의 컬렉션을 반환 하는 방법을 보여 줍니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6ca75-106">The following C# example shows how to return a collection of distinguished names in hexadecimal format.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
using System.DirectoryServices;  
...  
DirectorySearcher src = new DirectorySearcher("…");  
src.PropertiesToLoad = new string[] {ntSecurityDescriptor,…};  
src.ExtendedDN = ExtendedDN.HexString;  
SearchResultCollection res = src.FindAll();  
  
```
